summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 227W, page 17 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property located 120 feet north of N.E. 120th Street extending approximately 360 feet northward along the east side of 15th Avenue N.E., from Duplex Residence Medium Density (RD 7200) Zone to Multiple Residence Lot Density (RM 800) Zone. (Petition of Clay R. Williams, et al., C.F. 287602).
